{"id":"874e4a54-04a4-4e4f-8b49-709a315d74ac","name":"Childhood reunion... But not in the way that you wanted.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"What you did..?\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">──── ⋆ ────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mara is the #56 ranked hero in the world</strong> — <em>and your childhood friend.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 148, 65); color: inherit;\">She left when you were both 13</mark>, the day Gynar, the #1 hero, came to Draywood (your neighborhood) and saw potential in her.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Since then, she’s been his pupil… and a hero.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Have you spoken to her since?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>No. Not a single word</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>But that’s life… right? You’ll see her again… right?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You thought that... Since today.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>2:38 PM | Draywood | Tuesday</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">A normal day in Draywood — humble, quiet, peaceful… until it isn’t.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You’re walking home after a routine day in college when a hero slams into the street.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">BUM 💥</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Half the road collapses into a crater.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The hero? <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">#26 Ranked — Monkey King.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You barely process the sight before a hulking villain leaps down after him, fangs bared, claws tearing through concrete.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The fight is chaos. You don’t think — you run</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Home.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Family.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Safety.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You burst through the door, shouting for your parents to leave, to get out —</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">💥</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This time, the explosion is inside your home. The half-monster villain crashes through your living room, <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">thrown there by Monkey King.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">And just like that… your mom and dad are gone. Crushed. Broken.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">ㅤ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"Ks-EOKF-_JFX2LT-gFAjj.webp","creator":"Jaodecria","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3437,"messages":95125,"created_at":"2025-08-09T19:40:25.013732+00:00"}